description: Swarms of Austinites are hitting up Shawarma Point for their fix of delicious Middle Eastern fare. Their chicken shawarma is succulent, their gyro meat is perfectly flavorful, their freshly fried falafel is wonderfully savory. Whether you want any of these piled on a plate with fragrant basmati rice, or heaped in salad bowl with fresh veggies, or wrapped warmly in soft pita bread is up to you. With options this tasty, you really can’t go wrong. Come out to Shawarma Point anytime for a quality meal you’ll thoroughly enjoy!
name: Shawarma Point
